5 WHEREAS, the framers of the Constitution of the United States
6 empowered state legislatures to be guardians of liberty
7 against future abuses of power by the federal government; and
8
9 WHEREAS, the federal government has created a crushing
10 national debt through improper and imprudent spending; and
11
12 WHEREAS, the federal government has invaded the legitimate
13 roles of the states through the manipulative process of
14 federal mandates, many of which are unfunded mandates; and
